---
---
<section class="process section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="process-header">
      <h2>So einfach geht's</h2>
      <p>In 4 Schritten zu Ihrem perfekten Hörgerät</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Hörgerät auswählen</h3>
        <p>Vergleichen Sie unsere Modelle von Phonak, Oticon und Starkey und wählen Sie Ihr Wunschgerät.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-connector">
        <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24"><path d="M0 12 L30 12" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 4" fill="none"/><polygon points="30,6 40,12 30,18" fill="var(--color-primary)"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="3" width="15" height="13"/><polygon points="16 8 20 8 23 11 23 16 16 16 16 8"/><circle cx="5.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="18.5" cy="18.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Kostenlos zugesendet</h3>
        <p>Wir senden Ihnen das Hörgerät kostenlos nach Hause. Kein Geld wird abgebucht.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-connector">
        <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24"><path d="M0 12 L30 12" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 4" fill="none"/><polygon points="30,6 40,12 30,18" fill="var(--color-primary)"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>30 Tage testen</h3>
        <p>Testen Sie das Hörgerät in Ihrem Alltag. Unser Akustiker passt es per Ferntermin optimal an.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-connector">
        <svg width="40" height="24" viewBox="0 0 40 24"><path d="M0 12 L30 12" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4 4" fill="none"/><polygon points="30,6 40,12 30,18" fill="var(--color-primary)"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Erst dann zahlen</h3>
        <p>Zufrieden? Dann wird die Zahlung eingezogen. Nicht zufrieden? Kostenlos zurücksenden.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .process-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .process-grid {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .process-step {
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 240px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: -5px;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .process-step h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  .process-step p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .process-connector {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process-connector {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      padding-top: 0;
    }

    .process-step {
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
